.TH health
.SH NAME
health-req
.SH DESCRIPTION
The health requirement specifies the required value for the health for the object.
.SH PARAMETERS
.P
* value
.br
Specifies the required value of health points.
.P
* less
.br
Specifies whether actual health value should be less(true) or more(false) then value in the requirement.
.P
* charge
.br
Specifies wheter required health value should be taken from object health pool after requirement check.
.SH JSON EXAMPLE
.nf
{
    "value":100,
    "less":true,
    "charge":true
}
.SH XML EXAMPLE
.nf
<health-req value="100"
	    less="true"
	    charge="true"/>
.SH SEE ALSO
requirements, requirement/health-percent